{
  "title": "是鞍山，不是洛杉矶（一）",
  "coverAudio": "audio/ANSHAN1title.mp3",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "html": "当年台湾中学<span class=\"vocab\">地理<span class=\"tooltip\">dì lǐ — geography</span></span>课都像历史课，大陆地理内容都停留在1949年。各省<span class=\"vocab\">物产<span class=\"tooltip\">wù chǎn — local products</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">资源<span class=\"tooltip\">zī yuán — natural resources</span></span>、东北九省我们记得一清二楚。“钢都鞍山，煤都抚顺”，我总以为是东北最大的两座城市。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p1.mp3",
      "image": {
      "src": "img/p1.png"}
    },
    {
      "html": "2006年的电影《姨妈的后现代生活》里，斯琴高娃<span class=\"vocab\">扮演<span class=\"tooltip\">bàn yǎn — to play (a role/character)</span></span>的叶如棠，<span class=\"vocab\">抛夫弃女<span class=\"tooltip\">pāo fū qì nǚ — abandon husband and daughter</span></span>从东北回上海，<span class=\"vocab\">自称<span class=\"tooltip\">zì chēng — call oneself</span></span>从美国洛杉矶回来，过着她单身而文艺的生活。后来因为伤病入院，不得不联系家属。她十几年不见的<span class=\"vocab\">粗俗<span class=\"tooltip\">cū sú — vulgar; coarse</span></span>女儿来到医院<span class=\"vocab\">询问<span class=\"tooltip\">xún wèn — inquire</span></span>，护士本来挺<span class=\"vocab\">冷漠<span class=\"tooltip\">lěng mò — indifferent; apathetic</span></span>，一听是叶女士女儿，<span class=\"vocab\">秒变<span class=\"tooltip\">miǎo biàn — change instantly</span></span>热情“回来哒？”赵薇一愣“洛杉矶？<span class=\"vocab\">俺<span class=\"tooltip\">ǎn — I; me (dialect)</span></span>是鞍山的！”护士马上明白过来，又变得一脸<span class=\"vocab\">鄙视<span class=\"tooltip\">bǐ shì — despise; look down on</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "电影的最后，叶如棠回到鞍山，在市场<span class=\"vocab\">支<span class=\"tooltip\">zhī — set up, put up</span></span>起<span class=\"vocab\">小摊<span class=\"tooltip\">xiǎo tān — street stall</span></span>，面无表情地吃馒头。那画面<span class=\"vocab\">灰暗<span class=\"tooltip\">huī àn — dim; gloomy</span></span>的色调也<span class=\"vocab\">构成<span class=\"tooltip\">gòu chéng — constitute; form</span></span>我很长一段时间对鞍山的印象。但当我在一个晴朗的秋日午后，站在鞍山站前，看到的是一个色彩鲜明的城市，还真的有那么一点儿洛杉矶<span class=\"vocab\">内味儿<span class=\"tooltip\">nèi wèir — that kind of vibe (colloquial)</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山主城区是当年<span class=\"vocab\">伪满<span class=\"tooltip\">wěi mǎn — Manchukuo (puppet state)</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">时期<span class=\"tooltip\">shí qī — period; phase</span></span>常见的大城市<span class=\"vocab\">规划<span class=\"tooltip\">guī huà — plan; layout</span></span>：车站前有条大道，大道的<span class=\"vocab\">尽头<span class=\"tooltip\">jìn tóu — end; extremity</span></span>是一圆环，现在称为胜利广场。<span class=\"vocab\">围绕<span class=\"tooltip\">wéi rào — surround; revolve around</span></span>着圆环是各种风格的老<span class=\"vocab\">行政机关<span class=\"tooltip\">xíng zhèng jī guān — administrative agency</span></span>楼，<span class=\"vocab\">类似<span class=\"tooltip\">lèi sì — similar</span></span>这样的城市还有像长春、沈阳等地。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "胜利广场周边最引人<span class=\"vocab\">瞩目<span class=\"tooltip\">yǐn rén zhǔ mù — attract people's attention</span></span>的建筑是“焦耐院”，这名字有点<span class=\"vocab\">绕口<span class=\"tooltip\">rào kǒu — tongue-twisting</span></span>，其实<span class=\"vocab\">全称<span class=\"tooltip\">quán chēng — full name</span></span>是“中冶鞍山<span class=\"vocab\">焦化<span class=\"tooltip\">jiāo huà — coking</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">耐火<span class=\"tooltip\">nài huǒ — refractory</span></span>材料设计研究总院”，是中国<span class=\"vocab\">唯一<span class=\"tooltip\">wéi yī — only; sole</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">从事<span class=\"tooltip\">cóng shì — be engaged in; conduct</span></span>焦化、耐火材料工程设计的研究院。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "焦耐院是当年苏联<span class=\"vocab\">援建<span class=\"tooltip\">yuán jiàn — aid in construction</span></span>的，1954年<span class=\"vocab\">落成<span class=\"tooltip\">luò chéng — to be completed (building/project)</span></span>时是鞍山最高楼。现在焦耐院搬到大连去了，而这栋楼现在却成了<span class=\"vocab\">社交媒体<span class=\"tooltip\">shè jiāo méi tǐ — social media</span></span>上的<span class=\"vocab\">网红<span class=\"tooltip\">wǎng hóng — internet celebrity</span></span>楼。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山市区<span class=\"vocab\">地势<span class=\"tooltip\">dì shì — terrain</span></span>西平东高，过了圆环再往东走，是鞍山居住环境最好的地区─台<span class=\"vocab\">町<span class=\"tooltip\">tǐng — Japanese word for town/district</span></span>。这个地名<span class=\"vocab\">沿袭<span class=\"tooltip\">yán xí — follow (old practices)</span></span>自日文，意思就是“高地街区”。这一带街道，以<span class=\"vocab\">坡顶<span class=\"tooltip\">pō dǐng — hilltop</span></span>为中心向下<span class=\"vocab\">延伸<span class=\"tooltip\">yán shēn — extend; stretch</span></span>，<span class=\"vocab\">扇形<span class=\"tooltip\">shàn xíng — fan-shaped</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">布局<span class=\"tooltip\">bù jú — layout</span></span>，<span class=\"vocab\">仿效<span class=\"tooltip\">fǎng xiào — imitate; emulate</span></span>美式<span class=\"vocab\">住宅区<span class=\"tooltip\">zhù zhái qū — residential area</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">规划<span class=\"tooltip\">guī huà — plan; layout</span></span>，极其<span class=\"vocab\">幽静<span class=\"tooltip\">yōu jìng — quiet and secluded</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p7.mp3"
    }
  ],
